summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Walden Street from Renton Avenue to the west line of York Add. et al in the City of Seattle, by laying water mains under Ordinance No. 17464, creating Local Improvement District No. 1652 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
